ONE of <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland" target="_blank">Scotland's</a> top young <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acting" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acting" target="_blank">acting</a> talents is exposed today as a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crack_cocaine" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crack_cocaine" target="_blank">crack cocaine</a> and <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heroin" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heroin" target="_blank">heroin</a> dealerNick Ikunda 27 has been tipped for stardom after being named Best Actor at this month's <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAFTA_Scotland" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAFTA_Scotland" target="_blank">BAFTA Scotland</a> New <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_4" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_4" target="_blank">Talent</a> AwardsBut the Daily Record can reveal that his whole life is an actBetween <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/2006_in_film" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/2006_in_film" target="_blank">film</a> roles and auditions he ruins lives by peddling rocks of <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crack_cocaine" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crack_cocaine" target="_blank">crack</a> and tenner bags of <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heroin" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heroin" target="_blank">heroin</a> to desperate <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" target="_blank">addicts</a> on <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow" target="_blank">Glasgow</a>'s south sideKnown as âKashâ on the streets Ikunda can make more than &pound1000 a day from the vile tradeWe covertly filmed him taking money for crackOne drug user told our investigators how Ikunda sold him <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crack_cocaine" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crack_cocaine" target="_blank">crack</a> just days after he rubbed shoulders with <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Mullan" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Mullan" target="_blank">Peter Mullan</a> and Muriel Gray at the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAFTA_Scotland" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAFTA_Scotland" target="_blank">BAFTA</a> awardsAnd another <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" target="_blank">addict</a> said âHe splits his <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_%28magazine%29" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_%28magazine%29" target="_blank">time</a> between two lives and has two sets of friends â the guys he's involved with through his <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acting" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acting" target="_blank">acting</a> and his <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gangster" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gangster" target="_blank">gangster</a> palsâVery few of his customers will even know about his <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAFTA_Scotland" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAFTA_Scotland" target="_blank">BAFTA</a> winâThe <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" target="_blank">addict</a> added âMy big weakness is <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crack_cocaine" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crack_cocaine" target="_blank">crack</a> Once you've tried it you just want more and moreâIt wrecks your life You don't care what you have to do to get money to get moreâKash knows this He doesn't look like he touches the stuff himselfâIt's just a moneymaker for him That's what makes me sick He'll keep selling and selling until you have no money then phone you back later and ask if you want moreâWhat angers me is that he doesn't have to do this He's a clever guy and he can get a proper jobâBut he prefers to make easy money pushing <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crack_cocaine" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crack_cocaine" target="_blank">crack</a>â The <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" target="_blank">addict</a> said Ikunda brags of links to <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/London" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/London" target="_blank">London</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gangster" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gangster" target="_blank">gangsters</a> and sells <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heroin" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heroin" target="_blank">heroin</a> as well as crackHe explained âHe went to Govan High School which is tough but he was trendy and popular so it was easy for him to make contactsâHe still has contacts in London that he gets <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drug" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drug" target="_blank">drugs</a> fromâHe knows <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crack_cocaine" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crack_cocaine" target="_blank">crack</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" target="_blank">addicts</a> will sometimes use <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heroin" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heroin" target="_blank">heroin</a> to bring them down from the effects The withdrawal can be terribleâIkunda is active around the Shawbridge high flats in the Shawlands area of GlasgowWe followed him as he dropped off <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drug" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drug" target="_blank">drugs</a> around <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow" target="_blank">Glasgow</a> in the days after his <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAFTA_Scotland" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/BAFTA_Scotland" target="_blank">BAFTA</a> winAnd we caught him redhanded by posing as a potential customer ringing his <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mobile_pho